title: (500) Days of Summer - Soundtrack [Complete with Bonus Tracks][2
description:
Soundtrack of (500) Days of Summer was released on July 14, 2009. The soundtrack peaked at #71 on the U.S. Billboard 200.
[Source: Wikipedia]
